summary: Leather Boots for UNP female body.
descriptionHtml:
Name: UNP Boots
Version: 1.0
Date: 04-27-2012
Category: Clothing
Requirements: Skyrim
Author: Petrovich

==========
Description
==========
Leather Boots for UNP female body.
This Boots can be crafted on any smithing forge.

==========
Installation
==========
1. Extract the files \"UNP Boots.esp\" and \"UNP Boots.bsa\" to Skyrim\\Data\\ folder.
2. Start Skyrim Launcher, click \'Data Files\', place a checkmark beside the \"UNP Boots.esp\".
3. Enjoy!

==========
Deinstallation
==========
1. Start Skyrim Launcher, click \'Data Files\', uncheck \"UNP Boots.esp\".
2. Delete \"UNP Boots.esp\" and \"UNP Boots.bsa\".

==========
Change Log
==========
1.0 - Initial release.

==========
Credits and thanks
==========
Thanks to Bethesda for creating Skyrim.

==========
Contact
==========

==========
